title: Highly Upgraded, Perfect Home Office Space!
posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Mike Miller | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', '2Br/1Ba -', 'Hwy 100, St. Louis Park, MN 55416', '$1799/mo', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage:', '945 sqft.', 'Bedrooms: 2', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Parking:', 'Garage Parking is $75/Monthly', 'Lease Duration:', '9-14 Months', 'Deposit:', '$400', 'Pets Policy:', 'Cats & Dogs OK (3 Pets Max)', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Property Type:', 'Apartment', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Featuring the perfect blend of luxury and convenience located next to Highway 100 and just minutes from downtown Minneapolis.', "With easy access to shopping and dining, you're sure to find some St. Louis Park hidden gems.", "Modern one- and two- bedroom floor plans are immediately available, and with standard amenities ranging from hardwood floors, spacious kitchens with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and lovely walkout balconies that'll make you feel right at home.", 'Pries and availability are subject to change.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', 'Walk-In Closets', 'Stainless Steel Kitchen Appliances', 'Granite Countertops & Islands', 'Spacious Kitchens & Bathrooms', 'Quality Hardware', 'Terrace/Balcony Available*', 'Full-size Laundry', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', 'Continental Breakfast Weekly', 'Full-Time Maintenance Staff', 'Professional, On-Site Management Team', 'Controlled Access', 'Grilling Areas', 'Clubroom with Culinary Kitchen', 'Heated Bike Parking', 'Heated Underground Parking', 'Pet Washing Station', 'Pizza & Lawn Bowling Green', 'Resident Business Center', 'Selected', 'Rooftop Terrace', 'Tanning Bed', 'Fitness Open 24 Hours', 'Dry Cleaning Services', 'Guest Suite Rental', 'Package Concierge Service', 'Black Car Service', 'Housekeeping Available', 'Resident Events', 'Contact info: Mike Miller', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info']
